[02:56] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'image of the character and ask for a voice prompt. And then you just iterate and refine the prompt until you find one that you like. It\'s actually pretty easy. So, does it work? Mostly. Uh, I\'m going to show you the results. For my'

[03:09] [scene:talk]
